{"tid":688553,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"好想戒賭","createTime":"2018-06-03T10:39:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-08T10:47:28.000Z","uid":157720,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e9438f978fc7344289d42ba8585fc6532ab0321b","tid":688553,"uid":157720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T10:39:52.000Z","msg":"對唔住，我真係好想戒賭<br />\n我覺得令屋企人己經好失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n覺得自己好冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n差出面成百個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇人有戒賭既手機wallpaper<br />\n可以比我提醒下自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果可以<br />\n可唔可以有提醒慳錢的wallpaper<br />\n比我得閒轉下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n施主有圖 我一定廣為傳播 做福萬民<br />\n功德無量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94460956285758e61b22e2b2c628f2694863f6c6","tid":688553,"uid":157720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T10:43:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/03/184312_87001e4b797626c141323ef734bfbbd0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F03%2F184312_87001e4b797626c141323ef734bfbbd0.png&h=986815d3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2fd45cf16d179be96702a08a1a41f2823fa09bbc","tid":688553,"uid":19920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T10:44:59.000Z","msg":"百個好小姐"},{"pid":"76b49cd9ad18c1c1850fff72956a55e05